sg":"你太低估人類嘅創作力、無聊程度。自古以來就好多人吹水嚟呃呃騙騙。另外有啲係因為無聊吹水，喜歡喺朋友面前吹牛，顯得自己好L勁咁。亦有好多因為精神病而睇到幻覺，吸毒都有幻覺。有啲人搞唔清楚現實同幻想。"},{"pid":"14841302998dfe6295e08f55289fe857bc247c36","tid":988201,"uid":155558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"叫個牧師同KOEI 合作出返隻驅鬼無雙。"},{"pid":"d4a211eec15f237ce0c5874b201a75a697599c90","tid":988201,"uid":60716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:59:57.000Z","msg":"姐係話叫人去旅行唔好祈禱?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c188f0e671fc4d2968f2635b43ca4c6afede52","tid":988201,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"結果當事人在韓國祈禱時，發覺有一道力從尾龍骨衝入身體，自此被十多萬隻鬼上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9735f3cbe60dce83561dc7e225c91cbfca84e4b3","tid":988201,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14841302998dfe6295e08f55289fe857bc247c36","tid":988201,"uid":155558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"叫個牧師同KOEI 合作出返隻驅鬼無雙。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8RZAm5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8RZAm5.jpg&h=a5af1b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你講呢隻呀？"}]}